1.  background-position: top; 
means when changing the image responsive or height or width, the top position remain same
and other position like center and bottom changes.

2.  clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 80%, 0 100%);
means the part of the image we want to clip it is having the four coordinated having all the 
direction of the image (x, y)